<title>JAPAN: Nippon Comsys alters rules for share repurchase.</title>
<headline>Nippon Comsys alters rules for share repurchase.</headline>
<dateline>TOKYO 1997-06-27</dateline>
<text>
<p>Nippon Comsys Corp said on Friday that it had decided at an annual shareholders' meeting to change company rules in order to carry out share repurchases.</p>
<p>The telecommunications engineering company said in a statement that the upper limit of the repurchase would be 11 million ordinary shares.</p>
